to crash for the night,

10:58.625 --> 11:00.083
and I'm out of here by morning--

11:00.083 --> 11:01.083
Is everything okay?

11:01.667 --> 11:02.917
Dawson! H-hi.

11:04.125 --> 11:05.417
Yeah, everything's fine.
It was--

11:05.417 --> 11:06.917
Hey, how's it going?

11:06.917 --> 11:07.750
Billy Konrad.

11:10.166 --> 11:12.125
