of mine from New York.

11:13.125 --> 11:16.166
Uh...can I talk to you
for one second, Dawson?

11:16.166 --> 11:17.083
Yeah.

11:18.250 --> 11:19.792
JEN: [WHISPERING]
Look, I know this
is kind of awkward,

11:19.792 --> 11:20.959
but would it be okay tonight

11:20.959 --> 11:22.959
